Voyager New Moves

Blustery Terrain

Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
10 0 Un-grounds battlers and weakens sound moves.

Details

-Weakens sound-based moves by 50%

-Un-grounds all battlers so that they are immune to ground

-Boosts flying-type damage by 30%

-Doubles the speed of Pokemon that can learn Fly

-Boosts the power of 'Wind' moves (Razor Wind, Gust, Wing Attack, Blizzard, Aeroblast, Powder Snow, Icy Wind, Air Cutter, Silver Wind, Air Slash, Ominous Wind, Hurricane, Glaciate, Fairy Wind)
